    </steps>
    <result>
      <ul id="ul_09140766">
        <li>If there are no gaps, click <b>Finish</b>.</li>
        <li>If there are gaps or the pattern is faint, clean the print head.</li>
        <li>If almost the entire pattern is missing, click <b>Finish</b>and perform a Power Cleaning.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you don’t see any improvement after cleaning the print head up to 3 times, turn off the product and wait at least 12 hours. Then run a nozzle check and try cleaning the print head again. If quality still does not improve, run a Power Cleaning.</p>
    </result>
